social_posts.post_text:
This Sunday for #mycausemycleats I’ll be representing Duchenne Muscular Dystrophy awareness. I met Logan while attending the University of Iowa and continue to be grateful for our friendship over the years. I'm excited to continue raising awareness for MDA with my cleats to generate funds toward their mission. MDA's efforts have enabled the approvals of new treatments that are transforming the lives of people with neuromuscular diseases, and I know that together, the more funds we raise, the more we can achieve with our shared mission of supporting families involved with MDA.

December 7-17 these cleats will be auctioned with proceeds going to Parent Project Muscular Dystrophy for Duchenne research.
Practice makes perfect! Thanks Dr. Lana McDermott, @westsidedentaldecorah, and staff for making my @invisalign journey such a breeze, hard not to smile at these results! #ad #InvisalignSmiles
